# FitOwn Planning Docs

When editing planning files:

- Index lives at @docs/planning/README.md — update links if adding plans
- Each module plan uses: Objective → Features (checkboxes) → Files to Create → Acceptance Criteria
- Scope changes go in @docs/planning/PRODUCT.md first, then sync roadmap and module plans
- Wireframe reference: @docs/MASGARTI's Fit Tech.html
- Extracted sources: `docs/extracted/` (regenerate via `python3 scripts/extract-docs.py`)

Nested guide: @docs/planning/AGENTS.md
